reviews.review_text: fantastic recording of a great show! Since I was fortunate to have been at this show, I am so thankful that this fantastic recording is available on the archive!  And yes, those locomotive horns are incredibly loud! They can be heard starting at about 8:30 on Jam!  And they still make me jump!  Overall a great show too!  And kudos to Mr. Sacks for this magnificent addition to the archive!
Brings me back Still remember thinking a train was coming through the stadium when they blared the air horns the first time!
